That's it. You don't understand.

32:34.410 --> 32:36.703
Nobody, nobody talks to me like that.

32:36.871 --> 32:38.330
You understand?

32:38.539 --> 32:40.040
-Yes, I do.
-That's it.

32:40.208 --> 32:41.375
Let's do it. l'm ready.

32:41.542 --> 32:43.418
You don't hear the word "no" very often.

32:43.628 --> 32:46.880
I hear it all the time,
only it's more, "No, please, no, no."

32:47.548 --> 32:49.216
I'm here for two more days.

32:49.384 --> 32:52.678
When I get back to New York,
I'll treat you exclusively.

32:52.887 --> 32:54.680
For two weeks.

32:54.847 --> 32:56.932
I just don't know what
to tell my patients.

32:57.141 --> 32:58.892
-You want me to clear your schedule?
-Oh, no.

32:59.060 --> 33:01.853
It would be my honor to do that.
My pleasure. Jimmy?

33:02.021 --> 33:04.523
No. No, not Jimmy.
I will do this myself.

33:04.732 --> 33:05.857
-You sure?
-Positive.

33:06.067 --> 33:07.734
I will see you in New York.

33:07.902 --> 33:10.904
Okay. Want one of them?

33:11.114 --> 33:12.239
BEN: No, thanks.
VlTTI: Sure?

33:12.407 --> 33:14.408
BEN:
That's very kind of you, but l....

33:14.575 --> 33:16.743
Want to give a little sta minch?

33:17.412 --> 33:18.620
You sure?

33:19.664 --> 33:20.956
The pause that refreshes.

33:21.165 --> 33:22.916
I don't-- No, l really....

33:23.084 --> 33:24.209
You're on vacation.

33:24.377 --> 33:26.253
I'm also about to get married...

33:26.421 --> 33:28.922
...so l'd like to go back
to my hotel and....

33:29.132 --> 33:31.425
Good night.
I'll see you in New York.

33:31.718 --> 33:34.594
You. Hey, Doc. You.

33:34.762 --> 33:36.346
I'm going to see a lot of you.

33:37.223 --> 33:40.267
Ben? Where were you?

33:40.476 --> 33:42.436
My God, l woke up
and you were gone!

33:42.645 --> 33:45.313
There was no note or anything!
I was out of my mind!

33:45.523 --> 33:47.774
I walked all over the hotel
looking for you.

33:47.984 --> 33:51.069
I even ate a Rice Krispy Treat.
I almost called the police.

33:51.279 --> 33:54.156
No, don't call the police.
I'll tell you the truth.

33:54.365 --> 33:56.283
I had a patient emergency.

33:56.492 --> 33:58.577
You have patients in Florida?

33:58.786 --> 34:02.456
One. He followed me from New York.
I had to go, trust me.

34:02.665 --> 34:04.624
My God. Who is this patient?

34:06.794 --> 34:10.338
Paul Vitti.

34:10.798 --> 34:13.884
-Paul Vitti? Mafia Paul Vitti?
-Yeah.

34:14.510 --> 34:15.969
Yes.

34:16.137 --> 34:20.307
Oh, my God. Oh, my God.

34:20.975 --> 34:23.477
Listen. lt's not like
he's a regular patient.

34:23.686 --> 34:25.645
-He's got problems.
-Well, yeah.

34:25.813 --> 34:28.523
He thinks that l'm treating him.
It's crazy.

34:28.691 --> 34:30.317
-So you're not treating him?
-No.

34:30.485 --> 34:31.735
Tell me you're not.

34:31.944 --> 34:33.153
I'm not treating him.

34:33.321 --> 34:36.364
It's scary. You don't want
someone like that in your life.

34:36.574 --> 34:39.451
I've covered the mob down here.
I've seen what they do.

34:39.660 --> 34:42.788
He and l spoke about it.
He understood. lt's over.

34:42.997 --> 34:45.123
-You're sure?
-Absolutely.

34:45.750 --> 34:47.125
Okay.

34:47.293 --> 34:49.002
I was so worried.

34:49.212 --> 34:51.338
I thought maybe you got scared or...

34:51.506 --> 34:53.006
...saw an ex-girlfriend
or something.

34:53.174 --> 34:55.509
-Oh, no, no.
-Well, l don't know.

34:56.385 --> 34:57.928
-l love you.
-l love you.

34:58.137 --> 35:01.348
I'm sorry, but everything's
going to be okay.

35:03.684 --> 35:05.685
WOMAN [SlNGING OVER SPEAKERS]:
It's such a good vibration

35:05.853 --> 35:08.230
MAN: Give her a big hand! Let's hear it!
How about that?

35:08.397 --> 35:09.773
[CROWD APPLAUDlNG]

35:09.941 --> 35:11.733
LAURA:
Ooh, wow.

35:12.944 --> 35:15.570
That was great!
Come on, get into it.

35:16.239 --> 35:18.281
I don't understand.
They splash in the water.

35:18.449 --> 35:19.699
They eat fish.

35:19.867 --> 35:21.535
This is not a big stretch
for a whale.

35:21.702 --> 35:22.744
Stop it.

35:22.912 --> 35:25.038
We're having fun, right?

35:25.206 --> 35:28.125
I'm not having as much fun
as it looks like l am.

35:28.376 --> 35:31.128
I'm pretending, because we
have to bond and all.

35:35.883 --> 35:41.388
WOMAN: As l was saying, a little snack
for her might be, oh, 50 pounds of mackerel.

35:42.723 --> 35:44.057
There she goes!

35:47.770 --> 35:50.564
I'm going to get a hot dog.
Anybody want anything?

35:50.731 --> 35:52.274
-l'll go with you.
-No, it's fine.

35:52.483 --> 35:55.318
You're pretending to have a good time.
I don't want to spoil that.

35:55.570 --> 35:56.778
I'll be right back.

35:57.029 --> 35:59.072
You think those whales
piss in that water?

35:59.282 --> 36:03.285
I think they use the men's room
next door to the Burger King.

36:03.452 --> 36:04.494
Dummy.

36:04.704 --> 36:06.872
-What's going on?
-Mr. Vitti wants to see you.

36:07.081 --> 36:09.708
-ls this a joke?
-You're an employee of Mr. Vitti's...

36:09.917 --> 36:12.335
...which means you're on call
24 hours a day...

36:12.503 --> 36:14.004
...just like the rest of us.

36:14.255 --> 36:15.589
I'm sorry. He and l discussed--

36:15.756 --> 36:18.925
We discussed this, and l agreed
to see him in New York.

36:19.093 --> 36:20.093
That's it.

36:20.261 --> 36:23.221
Dr. Momma-Luke, listen to me.
It is what it is.

36:23.431 --> 36:25.891
If he wants you sooner,
you go sooner.

36:26.058 --> 36:27.434
That's it. Yeah.

36:27.602 --> 36:28.852
No. I am not going.

36:29.061 --> 36:31.605
And if either one of you
bother me again...

36:31.814 --> 36:33.273
...l won't treat him at all.

36:33.441 --> 36:34.608
Do you understand that?

36:34.775 --> 36:35.859
[SPEAKS IN lTALIAN]

36:36.027 --> 36:38.486
It's over! End of story.

36:39.322 --> 36:41.531
MAN:
Look at the size of this one.

36:41.949 --> 36:43.950
Jesus Christ!

36:45.786 --> 36:47.204
It's feeding time.

36:49.582 --> 36:51.291
BEN: They threw me in
the shark tank, Paul.

36:51.459 --> 36:53.084
VlTTI:
They were trying to make a point.

36:53.294 --> 36:55.337
That you're scary?
Believe me, l get it.

36:55.504 --> 36:56.546
You're in a mood.

36:56.756 --> 36:59.299
I get that way when
a shark tries to chew on my ass.

36:59.508 --> 37:02.219
-We had an agreement.
-We did, but I had an episode.

37:02.428 --> 37:05.430
I didn't have a panic attack,
but I started panicking...

37:05.640 --> 37:07.641
...thinking I might get one.
Is that weird?

37:07.850 --> 37:10.602
I am redefining "weird"
on an hourly basis.

37:10.811 --> 37:12.562
MOONY: What's he doing?
TINO: I don't know.

37:12.813 --> 37:15.190
-He's talking with some guy.
MOONY: Can you hit him?

37:15.399 --> 37:18.526
TINO: He's got fat Jelly and
his partner Jimmy Boots with him.

37:18.736 --> 37:21.780
I could do it with a rifle and scope,
but I don't have that with me.

37:21.989 --> 37:22.989
MOONY:
Just get him.

37:23.199 --> 37:25.325
TINO: You told me to take care of him,
I'll do it.

37:25.493 --> 37:27.661
BEN: What were you thinking
when you got anxious?

37:27.828 --> 37:30.163
Let's get out of here.
We're being watched.

37:30.373 --> 37:33.166
Don't look.
There's feds up there watching us.

37:33.334 --> 37:35.126
How do you know that?

37:35.294 --> 37:36.962
I'm a criminal. lt's my job.

37:38.172 --> 37:40.173
RICCl:
Who's the new face?

37:40.967 --> 37:43.426
STEADMAN:
Maybe he's Vitti's new consigliere.

37:43.678 --> 37:46.721
PROVANO: Whoever this guy is,
he must be important to the family.

37:46.931 --> 37:49.683
STEADMAN: Put his picture on the wire,
see what you come up with.

37:54.146 --> 37:58.191
Normally, a patient wouldn't have
a vat of Scotch during a session.

38:00.152 --> 38:03.863
That's interesting. l'll have to
remember it if l'm ever on Jeopardy.

38:04.031 --> 38:05.407
BEN:
Tell me about your father.

38:05.616 --> 38:08.243
VlTTI:
My father. Well, my father....

38:08.452 --> 38:09.953
Let's sit here.

38:10.746 --> 38:11.997
My father.

38:13.374 --> 38:15.792
A big man in the neighborhood.
Everybody loved him.

38:16.002 --> 38:17.919
Very well-respected, God rest his soul.

38:18.129 --> 38:19.629
He passed away?

38:19.839 --> 38:22.799
I just like saying "God rest his soul."
Of course he passed away.

38:23.009 --> 38:24.718
I was about 1 2 at the time.

38:24.885 --> 38:26.219
How did he die?

38:26.721 --> 38:28.888
It was a sudden thing.
A heart attack.

38:29.056 --> 38:31.474
How was the relationship?
Were you close?

38:31.684 --> 38:32.976
Eh, we were pretty close.

38:33.185 --> 38:35.437
We weren't getting along great
right then.

38:35.604 --> 38:37.147
Why is that?

38:37.315 --> 38:39.941
I was hanging out in the neighborhood.
I had a borgata.

38:40.109 --> 38:41.401
What is that?

38:41.569 --> 38:44.070
A kid gang, nothing big.
But he didn't like that.

38:44.238 --> 38:45.488
-He didn't approve.
-No, no.

38:45.656 --> 38:47.991
He slapped me around
a couple of times.

38:48.326 --> 38:49.492
And what?

38:49.702 --> 38:50.994
And then he died.

38:51.579 --> 38:53.413
How'd that make you feel?

38:53.581 --> 38:56.124
It felt great, wonderful.
How'd it make me feel?

38:56.292 --> 38:57.417
Think about it.

38:57.585 --> 39:00.795
Were you angry?
Were you afraid? Sad?

39:00.963 --> 39:02.964
Maybe all those things.

39:03.132 --> 39:04.758
Any feelings of guilt?

39:04.925 --> 39:06.301
About what? I didn't kill him.

39:06.510 --> 39:08.178
I know that,
I'm just speculating...

39:08.346 --> 39:12.349
...that maybe in some way
you may have wanted him to die.

39:12.558 --> 39:14.017
Why would l want him to die?

39:14.226 --> 39:17.145
You said you were fighting.
He slapped you around...

39:17.355 --> 39:19.564
...because you rebelled
against his authority.

39:19.774 --> 39:21.608
Maybe some unresolved
Oedipal conflict.

39:21.776 --> 39:23.443
English, English.

39:23.652 --> 39:27.530
Oedipus was a Greek king who killed
his father and married his mother.

39:27.698 --> 39:28.823
Fucking Greeks.

39:28.991 --> 39:31.326
It's an instinctual developmental drive.

39:31.494 --> 39:33.661
The young boy wants to
replace his father...

39:33.829 --> 39:36.289
...so that he can
totally possess his mother.

39:36.457 --> 39:38.792
Are you saying
I wanted to fuck my mother?

39:38.959 --> 39:42.003
-lt's a primal fantasy.
-Have you ever seen my mother?

39:42.213 --> 39:44.464
-Are you out of your mind?
-lt's Freud!

39:44.632 --> 39:47.509
Freud's a sick fuck, and you are
too for bringing it up.

39:47.676 --> 39:49.636
-lt's--
-Ugh!

39:51.222 --> 39:54.516
BEN: Can l be honest?
I don't think l can call you Dad.

39:54.725 --> 39:57.477
So, what do l call you?
Do I call you Scott?

39:57.645 --> 39:59.354
My friends call me Captain.

40:00.272 --> 40:01.815
-Captain?
-Yeah, Captain.

40:01.982 --> 40:03.483
Captain.

40:03.651 --> 40:05.944
Want another drink?
I'm definitely having eight or nine.

40:06.112 --> 40:07.987
I'd like a morphine and soda.

40:08.155 --> 40:10.073
I'm shaking.

40:10.241 --> 40:13.827
Shall we go to our table?
Come on, Michael.

40:13.994 --> 40:15.412
Hey. Hey.

40:15.579 --> 40:16.871
Señor Sobel.

40:20.334 --> 40:21.501
How you doing?

40:23.170 --> 40:24.671
Honey, it's the Vittis.

40:24.839 --> 40:26.881
My God. Yeah.

40:28.217 --> 40:31.302
Everybody's happy,
everybody's smiling. This is nice.

40:31.470 --> 40:33.346
You Paul Vitti, the mobster.

40:35.099 --> 40:37.225
Now, is that polite? Eh?

40:37.393 --> 40:39.727
Is that being nice?
I'm trying to be nice.

40:39.937 --> 40:42.897
Do I walk up to you and say
you're so-and-so, the hard-on?

40:43.941 --> 40:46.067
This is Laura's father,
the captain.

40:46.277 --> 40:48.069
VlTTI:
I'm very, very sorry.

40:48.279 --> 40:49.404
Excuse us.

40:51.866 --> 40:53.950
I heard about the wedding.
Here you go.

40:54.160 --> 40:57.454
A little something for
the bride and groom. God bless.

40:57.830 --> 40:58.955
We can't accept this.

40:59.123 --> 41:00.832
-Yes, you can.
-Thank you.

41:01.000 --> 41:04.419
I'm just going to borrow this guy.
I'll bring him right back.

41:04.628 --> 41:06.379
And then you'll leave us alone.

41:06.547 --> 41:09.466
I'll leave you alone.
I got to talk to you.

41:11.302 --> 41:12.969
Two minutes.
Two minutes.

41:13.179 --> 41:15.763
Wait over there.
Don't listen to what we say.

41:15.973 --> 41:17.432
My ears are sealed.

41:17.641 --> 41:19.559
I had a really weird dream
last night.

41:19.727 --> 41:22.729
I feel like I'm having one now.
Why'd you interrupt my party?

41:22.938 --> 41:25.482
You're really very rigid
about certain things.

41:25.691 --> 41:27.025
Did you know that?

41:27.234 --> 41:29.569
All right,
tell me about your dream.

41:29.737 --> 41:31.362
I'm asleep.

41:31.572 --> 41:34.199
I hear a baby crying.
I go to the refrigerator.

41:34.408 --> 41:35.992
I get him a bottle of milk.

41:36.202 --> 41:37.994
I bring the bottle of milk to him...

41:38.204 --> 41:39.537
...l see the milk is black.

41:39.747 --> 41:42.373
JELLY: That's fucking weird!
-Get out of here.

41:42.583 --> 41:44.250
-Get out of here.
-Sorry.

41:45.294 --> 41:48.421
What does that mean?
And no more filth about my mother.

41:48.589 --> 41:50.548
I don't know.
What does it mean to you?

41:51.425 --> 41:54.594
This is why I pay you? I say
something, you say it back to me?

41:54.803 --> 41:57.055
I could get Jelly to
do that for nothing.

41:57.264 --> 41:59.807
Get Jelly.
I'm going back to my party.

42:01.769 --> 42:03.937
All right.
I'm letting it go this time.

42:04.104 --> 42:07.232
Because you're getting married,
I'm going to let it go.

42:10.945 --> 42:13.905
Why don't you look over that way
before l bust your fucking head open?

42:14.073 --> 42:15.448
Jesus.

42:28.796 --> 42:32.131
I'm going to grab a bite to eat.
You want a sandwich?

42:32.633 --> 42:34.801
What kind of sandwich
ain't too fattening?

42:34.969 --> 42:36.594
A half a sandwich.

42:37.096 --> 42:39.055
I'll be back in a few minutes.

42:42.059 --> 42:43.977
[ELEVATOR DINGS]

42:44.144 --> 42:46.187
[SILENCED GUNSHOTS]

43:09.878 --> 43:12.505
Now, nod your head and smile.
Do it.

43:13.465 --> 43:15.174
Now, you listen to me, goombah.

43:15.342 --> 43:18.386
I know what your game is,
and you'd better call it quits.

43:18.554 --> 43:22.181
If you and your paisans
do anything to hurt my little girl...

43:22.391 --> 43:24.017
...l don't care who
your friends are...

43:24.184 --> 43:27.687
...l'll hunt you down like
the dog you are, and I'll kill you.

43:27.855 --> 43:29.272
Understand?

43:29.440 --> 43:31.232
Now, nod and smile.

43:31.775 --> 43:33.026
Congratulations.

43:36.697 --> 43:37.864
What was that about?

43:38.073 --> 43:41.784
Just guy stuff between
me and the captain.

43:45.372 --> 43:48.291
[CHATTERlNG ON TV]

44:00.971 --> 44:03.723
[SHOWER RUNNING]

44:20.741 --> 44:22.617
[YELLING]

44:46.892 --> 44:48.351
Shit!

44:51.188 --> 44:53.773
In sickness and in health,
from this day forth...

44:53.941 --> 44:55.942
-...as long as you both shall live?
-l--

44:56.110 --> 44:57.360
[GLASS SHATTERlNG]

44:57.528 --> 44:59.529
[SCREAMlNG]

45:00.239 --> 45:01.739
[PEOPLE SCREAMING]

45:01.907 --> 45:04.701
Ey-ey-ey-ey-ey.

45:05.244 --> 45:07.829
Bring Marie and
the kids right to the airport.

45:08.038 --> 45:11.791
Pull the car in the back of the hotel
and wait for us.

45:12.000 --> 45:13.042
JlMMY:
You got it, boss.

45:13.252 --> 45:15.878
That's it. That is it.
I have had it with you.

45:16.088 --> 45:17.130
-What happened?
-What happened?

45:17.339 --> 45:21.217
I just saw a man fall seven stories
into a platter of poached salmon!

45:21.427 --> 45:23.302
JELLY: Did he break anything?
-Everything!

45:23.470 --> 45:25.179
They're still pulling capers
out of him.

45:25.389 --> 45:29.225
People get depressed, they jump.
It's a tragedy, but it ain't my fault.

45:29.435 --> 45:31.060
You're telling me it was a suicide?

45:31.270 --> 45:33.813
I think he left a note.
Jelly, did they find it?

45:33.981 --> 45:35.940
No, but they will in a minute.

45:36.150 --> 45:38.276
Let me guess what it says:
"Life is bullshit.

45:38.485 --> 45:40.820
I can't fucking take it no more.
Signed, the dead guy."

45:40.988 --> 45:42.947
Hey. That's good, Doc.

45:43.157 --> 45:45.408
Enough talk.
We got to get out of here.

45:45.617 --> 45:47.201
There's feds all over.

45:47.411 --> 45:49.287
I'm going back to New York...

45:49.496 --> 45:52.290
...and l would suggest that
you do the same thing.

45:52.499 --> 45:54.292
Because they're probably
on to you too.

45:54.501 --> 45:56.544
On to me?
What are you talking about?

45:56.754 --> 46:00.214
Being an accessory to a murder
wasn't part of our understanding.

46:00.424 --> 46:02.133
I didn't kill nobody.

46:02.301 --> 46:04.177
I can't speak for
other people in the room.

46:04.344 --> 46:05.511
That guy tried to kill me.

46:05.679 --> 46:08.347
God forbid he did that
to somebody in my family.

46:08.515 --> 46:10.850
It would've been
a double or a triple tragedy.

46:11.018 --> 46:13.394
Trust me, in this case,
we're the good guys.

46:13.604 --> 46:15.104
LAURA:
Where is he?

46:15.856 --> 46:18.149
JlMMY: Where are you going?
-Don't touch me.

46:19.234 --> 46:20.693
How could you do that?

46:20.986 --> 46:22.779
Another country heard from.

46:23.322 --> 46:24.363
Wait downstairs.

46:24.531 --> 46:27.742
Why? Are they going to throw me
off the balcony too?

46:28.368 --> 46:30.870
You're upset and
you're upsetting me.

46:31.079 --> 46:32.163
Of course I'm upset!

46:32.372 --> 46:35.708
My wedding is ruined
because you've got problems!

46:35.876 --> 46:36.959
I got problems?

46:37.544 --> 46:38.586
Honey, please.

46:39.546 --> 46:42.381
I'm going to pack,
and then l'm going to New York.

46:42.591 --> 46:45.551
And l am getting married with you
or without you!

46:46.220 --> 46:48.346
With! With! l'm sorry, honey.

46:48.555 --> 46:51.891
It'll all work out. l promise.
Please?

46:52.851 --> 46:54.477
No, I hate you!

46:56.063 --> 46:58.147
Are you happy? Huh?
Are you happy?

46:58.357 --> 47:00.650
You know what you did?
You have ruined my life!

47:00.859 --> 47:02.735
Happy?
What are you talking about?

47:02.945 --> 47:05.238
You think I wanted this?
I'm a victim here.

47:05.405 --> 47:06.864
I can't believe this guy.

47:07.074 --> 47:09.325
He tries to kill me,
then whacks one of my guys.

47:09.535 --> 47:13.079
On top of that, he fucks up your wedding.
You know how upset I am?

47:13.247 --> 47:15.998
I'm so enraged, I don't know
what do to with myself!

47:16.208 --> 47:18.751
Plus, l'm trying to
get out of this hotel and--

47:18.919 --> 47:20.586
Are you listening to yourself?

47:20.796 --> 47:21.963
